creator: Swan Bitcoin
descriptionHtml:
Own your future - get started with a free Swan Bitcoin account today.

Swan specializes in Bitcoin, and Bitcoin only. Swan is more than just a place to buy BTC, we're a partner on your Bitcoin journey. Bitcoin is an exciting opportunity to get in early on better money and grow your wealth. It all starts with the Swan app.


WHY SWAN?

🟠 Easy & Instant Buys: Buy Bitcoin in seconds with a few taps. Swan's enterprise-grade custodians hold your BTC securely until you're ready to self-custody.
🟠 Recurring Buys: Invest regularly. Set an amount, choose daily, weekly or monthly, and we do the rest. Our savings plans are the no-stress way to accumulate Bitcoin.
🟠 Low Fees: Flat 0.99% fee for all orders. No spread. Our fees are up to 80% lower than other major exchanges.
🟠 Free Withdrawals: Absolutely free to withdraw your BTC because we promote self-custody - when you're ready for it.
🟠 Bitcoin Education: The Swan app is a great place to access Swan's vast and growing library of Bitcoin educational content.
🟠 Refer & Earn: Every person you refer through Swan Force gets $10 of Bitcoin, and you earn BTC each time they buy for an entire year.
🟠 Convenient & Secure: Set up price alerts. Hide your balances. Add biometric authentication for extra privacy and security. Monitor BTC's price and your portfolio. And much more. We're constantly adding new features.


SWAN: A BITCOIN FINANCIAL SERVICES COMPANY

🦢 Swan IRA provides a tax-advantaged solution for saving Bitcoin in retirement accounts.
🏢 Swan Private serves HNWIs and businesses, Swan offers tailored white-glove service for large purchases, treasury solutions, and employee Bitcoin benefits.
🛡️ Swan Vault is advanced Bitcoin security made simple. Clients can easily custody their own Bitcoin with peace of mind.
👨‍💼 Swan Advisor helps financial advisors make client Bitcoin allocations, backed by world-class custody and educational content.
🤝 Swan prides itself on exceptional client service, making Bitcoin accessible to all.
🏝️ Pacific Bitcoin Festival: An annual celebration of Bitcoin, Bitcoiners, and the bright orange future we're creating together. Brought to you by Swan and hosted in Los Angeles. All are welcome.


TRUSTED BY BITCOIN ENTHUSIASTS WORLDWIDE

Join 100,000+ users who choose Swan. Here's what clients are saying:

"Best Bitcoin App - ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐
Swan has to be the best way to stack sats. They have everything you need for your own DCA program or simple one time buy. They will even deliver your coins to you wallet automatically. They are experts at helping you gift Bitcoin to friends and family and are a fountain of great educational material. It doesn't get better than this." — Bitcoin4Life21, Swan App User

"Swan wins. - ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐
Swan has been the most reliable way to buy bitcoin over the years and their bitcoin-only mission puts them in a category of their own. They always exceed my expectations and the app experience is no different! Swan is the only exchange I feel comfortable recommending to friends and family." — Castomatic, Swan App User


ABOUT SWAN

Swan has been featured in: The New York Times, Forbes, The Wall St. Journal, Bitcoin Magazine, Yahoo! Finance, Barron's, CNBC, and more.

"Swan Bitcoin isn’t a crypto exchange. It’s a bitcoin accumulation platform... In short, Swan’s advantage is that it has lower fees than most other platforms, and better usability and customer service than most other platforms. I don’t know any platform that can claim a better combination of both fees and service, along with a sustainable business model. It comes with specialization." -Lyn Alden, Swan board member and author of Broken Money


OWN YOUR FUTURE. GET STARTED WITH SWAN TODAY

Need Help? https://help.swanbitcoin.com/

Privacy & Disclosures: https://www.swanbitcoin.com/privacy-policy/
descriptionShort: Buy, learn, and earn Bitcoin. The future of money.

descriptionHtml:
Let’s build Bitcoin wealth, together.

Swan isn't just another place to buy Bitcoin – we're your partner in building generational Bitcoin wealth. Our Bitcoin experts deliver personalized service to help you navigate Bitcoin with confidence. Swan gives you the tools and guidance to do it right.

WHY CHOOSE SWAN?
- Swan Guard: Enterprise-grade custody with SOC 2 Type 2 compliance at its core, Swan Guard protects your assets so you can focus on growing wealth.
- Swan Private: Our dedicated Bitcoin experts work tirelessly to build strong relationships with clients and understand the nuances of managing wealth in a world transformed by Bitcoin.
- Swan IRA: Hold actual Bitcoin in your retirement account. Open a new Traditional or Roth IRA, or transfer your existing retirement account to Swan. Swan can also assist with 401(k) rollovers.
- Swan Vault: Go further with your Bitcoin security with our institutional-grade cold storage solution.
- Instant Bitcoin Buys: Buy Bitcoin whenever you want. Use your bank account or wire transfer to buy immediately at the current market price.
- Recurring Buys: Set up automatic recurring daily, weekly, or monthly purchases. Build Bitcoin wealth while avoiding the stress of timing the market.
- Limit Orders: Name a price you’d like to pay for Bitcoin, and Swan will automatically buy when it hits that price.
- Free Withdrawals: We believe in Bitcoin self-custody. That's why we never charge withdrawal fees when you're ready to move your Bitcoin to your own wallet.

BEYOND THE BASICS
- Swan Private: Planning a larger allocation? Unlock white-glove service from Swan. Our dedicated team provides personalized support for large purchases and business treasury solutions. Get direct access to Bitcoin specialists who understand your unique requirements and can help implement tailored strategies for your wealth preservation goals.
- Swan IRA: Provides a tax-advantaged solution for saving Bitcoin in retirement accounts. Choose between Traditional and Roth IRAs with seamless transfers and rollovers from your existing retirement accounts. Our transparent fee structure keeps things simple.
- Swan Vault: Advanced Bitcoin cold-storage security made simple. Clients can easily custody their own Bitcoin with peace of mind. Our guided setup process and optional one-on-one specialist session ensure you're confident in your security. With features like 72-hour withdrawal holds and multi-signature protection, your Bitcoin stays safe even if you lose your keys.
AND MORE
- Enable biometric authentication and hide balances for extra privacy.
- Track all your accounts in one place.
